snippet.title: Impostor - Part 1 - Held prisoner by my spouse
snippet.description:
Welcome to Impostor, a game where our partner thinks we're...not who we once were. We're an impostor, they're convinced of that and so we end up tied up in the basement.

Can we survive this? Are we the real we or is she right and we're an impostor?

This game has several endings and I will show you only one. Please download the game and go discover more on your own! :)

I hope you enjoy.

Get the game here: https://melancholy-marionette.itch.io/impostor

Outro music: QubeSounds/Pixabay
